sources.title: Narcotics Squad (1957) PAUL KELLY
sources.description:
Stars: Paul Kelly, Cathy Downs, Regis Toomey
Writer/Director: Alexander J. Wells

After several high school get hooked on heroin, Lieutenant Lacey and the Narcotics Squad must bring the deadly drug peddlers to justice. (a.k.a Curfew Breakers)
